'''丹尼尔·沃德'''（{{lang-en|'''Daniel "Danny" Ward'''}}，{{bd|1991年|12月11日|catIdx=Daniel Ward}}）是[[英格兰|英格兰]][[足球|足球]][[运动员|运动员]]，司职[[前鋒_(足球)|前锋]]，现時效力[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈特斯菲]]。

==生平==
===俱乐部===
沃德2005年-2007年曾在[[利兹联足球俱乐部|利兹联]]接受青训，2007年转投[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|博尔顿]]。

2009年8月15日，沃德在博尔顿主场0比1输给[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|桑德兰]]的比赛第83分钟替补[[約翰·艾曼達|埃尔曼德]]出场，第一次代表博尔顿比赛<ref>[http://www.bwfc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,1004~49145,00.html Bolton 0-1 Sunderland] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bwfc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,1004~49145,00.html |date=20090901032841 }}{{en}}</ref>。11月26日，他被租借到[[英甲|英甲]]球队[[斯文登足球俱乐部|斯文登]]一个月，由於表現出色，獲延長借用至球季結束<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5910004,00.html |title=Robins extend Ward stay |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-02-01 |accessdate=2010-02-02 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010510/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5910004,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，期間上陣32場及射入9球，包括附加賽準決賽兩回合對[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:查尔顿竞技; zh-hk:查爾頓;}-]]各射入1球，並在[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]射入決勝球將球隊帶入決賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8691240.stm |title=Swindon Town's play-off final delights Danny Ward |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-05-19 |accessdate=2010-09-12 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307192141/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8691240.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，惟決賽在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]0-1不敵[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:米尔沃尔; zh-hk:米禾爾;}-]]而失去升班機會。

2010年9月7日沃德與保頓簽署三年新約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/8976863.stm |title=Danny Ward signs three-year Bolton contract |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-09-07 |accessdate=2010-09-12 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307022107/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/8976863.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，9月10日獲外借到[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]至翌年1月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/coventry_city/8988031.stm |title=Coventry City sign Bolton Wanderers winger Danny Ward |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-09-10 |accessdate=2010-09-12 |archive-date=2010-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100913044533/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/coventry_city/8988031.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月14日為高雲地利上陣6場後，被送返保頓動[[手術|手術]]治療[[腹股沟疝|腹股沟疝]]，預計需休養1個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ccfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10269~2184422,00.html |title=Ward returns to Bolton |publisher=[[考文垂足球俱乐部|''ccfc.co.uk'']] |date=2010-10-14 |accessdate=2010-10-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101019015748/http://www.ccfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10269~2184422%2C00.html |archivedate=2010-10-19 }}</ref>。

2011年3月15日沃德被外借到[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲爾德]]直到球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/huddersfield_town/9425068.stm |title=Huddersfield Town sign Bolton winger Danny Ward on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-15 |accessdate=2011-03-16 |archive-date=2018-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180926052132/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/huddersfield_town/9425068.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於當晚作客1-0擊敗[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|賓福特]]下半場後補上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/9422282.stm |title=Brentford 0-1 Huddersfield |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-15 |accessdate=2011-03-16 |archive-date=2020-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721111237/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/9422282.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。期間協助球隊晉級升班附加賽決賽，上陣10場射入4球。

2011年7月11日沃德正式轉投[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲爾德]]，簽約三年，並有一年優先，轉會費沒有透露<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.htafc.com/page/NewsDetail/0,,10312~2390664,00.html |title=WARDY RETURNS! |publisher=[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|''htafc.com'']] |date=2011-07-11 |accessdate=2011-08-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715211844/http://www.htafc.com/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10312~2390664%2C00.html |archivedate=2011-07-15 }}</ref>。

